ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Title: Download service (WCS) of data from the French numerical weather prediction limited area model. Resolution 0.025 degree over France. Steps 0 to 42h.
ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Abstract: The service allows to download in grid point analysis and forecast data from the limited area French numerical weather prediction model (named Arome) in grid point.
